    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Valenti <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erano</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>LVII et Iuliae Iuliae <expan><abbr>coni</abbr><ex>ugi</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>eius <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXVI et <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> Valen<lb break="no" n="4"/>tinae filiae eorum <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX <lb n="5"/>et <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Cassiano <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Praetorinus pa<supplied reason="lost">renti</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>bus et sorori c<supplied reason="lost">arissim<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="8"/>fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei teilweise aneinanderpassende Fragmente des Inschriftfeldes einer Grabstele, in Sekundärverwendung als Deckplatte eines Sarkophages gefunden. Die Maßangabe bezieht sich auf beide Fragmente. Zwischen Z. 3 u. 4. schräg unter dem ersten L von Z. 3 ein weiteres L, wohl irrtümlich eingehauen. Zeile 1: AN-Ligatur; Zeile 4: XXX-Ligatur. Zeile 2: Iuliae mglw. statt Iullae. Zeile 7: c[arissimis] oder c[arissimae].</p>
            </div>
